"Once the things that have to be done will be done, psychology in the short term will return to one of the confrontations," he said.
Wehner also expressed his widely shared scepticism that civilization would lead to true cooperation.
"I consider most of what is going on between today and 2012 as a pre-show or a shadow-boxing compared to the main event of 2012, he said.
